 {"id":"beads_rust-2jsm","title":"Integrate rich output into doctor command","description":"## Command: br doctor

### Traffic Level: LOW
Diagnostic and health check command.

### Current Implementation
Location: src/cli/commands/doctor.rs
Output: List of checks with pass/fail

### Integration Steps
1. Show checks as they run (progressive)
2. Use checkmarks/X for pass/fail
3. Add detailed explanations for failures
4. Summary panel at end

### Visual Enhancement
```
