### Status Indicators
- ✓ Green: check passed
- ⚠ Yellow: warning (non-blocking)
- ❌ Red: failed (critical)

### Progressive Display
In Rich mode, show spinner while each check runs, then replace with result. Creates satisfying "checking..." effect.

### Agent Mode
Simple pass/warn/fail counts and exit code.

